WEBVTT

01:43.259 --> 01:45.970
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.100 --> 01:48.950
[Episode 22]

01:53.600 --> 01:56.289
So Li Ruonan's mother is still nowhere to be found.

01:53.820 --> 01:57.000
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

01:59.270 --> 01:59.710
Director.

01:59.759 --> 02:00.910
We've been asking around everywhere these days,

02:02.150 --> 02:03.250
but no one knows

02:03.280 --> 02:04.330
when Li Ruonan's mother

02:04.380 --> 02:05.820
disappeared.

02:05.950 --> 02:07.120
From what I know, those in the neighborhood

02:07.150 --> 02:08.100
don't interact with each other a lot.

02:08.229 --> 02:09.330
They suddenly found out one day

02:09.360 --> 02:10.240
that her house became empty.

02:12.580 --> 02:13.930
What about Li Ruonan?

02:14.680 --> 02:15.350
She didn't confess anything.

02:16.710 --> 02:17.550
Director Xing.

02:17.870 --> 02:18.980
When people like Li Ruonan

02:19.010 --> 02:19.930
get arrested,

02:19.960 --> 02:21.110
they're determined to die.

02:21.340 --> 02:22.480
So it's very hard to get them to talk.

02:23.150 --> 02:24.290
Based on the last interrogation,

02:24.320 --> 02:25.360
we speculated that

02:25.579 --> 02:27.650
Li Ruonan values her mother very much.

02:28.270 --> 02:28.880
But at the moment,

02:28.910 --> 02:30.579
we have too few clues.

02:30.790 --> 02:32.040
It took us a lot of time

02:32.070 --> 02:33.520
to follow that clue and try to find her mother,

02:33.530 --> 02:34.930
but we achieved nothing.

02:36.270 --> 02:37.110
Director Xing.

02:37.630 --> 02:38.700
During our

02:38.750 --> 02:39.840
investigation this time,

02:40.310 --> 02:41.970
I suddenly feel that

02:42.310 --> 02:43.390
there's one person we can't overlook.

02:44.310 --> 02:45.450
It was

02:45.910 --> 02:46.790
eight years ago.

02:47.070 --> 02:48.610
There was a girl who committed suicide

02:49.190 --> 02:50.220
named Deng Man.

02:50.910 --> 02:51.730
Yes.

02:51.870 --> 02:53.640
I agree with Captain Jiang's opinion.

02:54.870 --> 02:55.760
Both victims

02:55.790 --> 02:57.500
had some direct

02:57.560 --> 02:58.980
or indirect connections with Deng Man.

02:59.370 --> 03:01.260
Wang Qianqian died in the same lake

03:01.330 --> 03:02.510
where Deng Man drowned back then,

03:01.400 --> 03:04.590
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

03:03.150 --> 03:04.330
and Ding Jing

03:04.420 --> 03:06.410
and Deng Man used to be classmates.

03:07.310 --> 03:08.270
Now, we have absolutely no idea

03:08.310 --> 03:09.470
what motivated Li Ruonan

03:09.550 --> 03:11.730
to kill Wang Qianqian,

03:11.990 --> 03:13.360
and it's even harder to explain why

03:13.390 --> 03:15.060
after killing Wang Qianqian,

03:15.110 --> 03:16.950
she went through so much trouble

03:17.030 --> 03:18.079
to carry Wang Qianqian into the lake

03:18.110 --> 03:20.220
where Deng Man drowned.

03:20.760 --> 03:21.600
What special significance

03:21.630 --> 03:22.630
does this lake have?

03:22.910 --> 03:23.680
All these

03:23.710 --> 03:24.730
are yet to be known.

03:25.950 --> 03:26.860
So,

03:27.400 --> 03:29.710
I want to re-investigate

03:29.829 --> 03:31.880
the case of Deng Man's suicide

03:32.150 --> 03:33.850
to see if we missed anything.

03:36.790 --> 03:38.410
So you suspect

03:38.550 --> 03:39.970
there was something wrong with that case back then?

03:40.110 --> 03:42.260
Based on the current situation,

03:42.710 --> 03:44.070
I think Deng Man's

03:44.110 --> 03:45.270
suicide case

03:46.150 --> 03:46.960
was probably not so simple

03:46.990 --> 03:48.230
as suicide.

03:52.430 --> 03:53.030
Okay.

03:53.990 --> 03:55.450
Just go for it.

03:55.950 --> 03:56.950
You have my full support.

03:57.240 --> 03:57.980
Also,

03:58.470 --> 03:59.360
don't forget

03:59.470 --> 04:00.840
to mobilize the power of the people

04:01.030 --> 04:02.450
to help us solve the case.

04:02.910 --> 04:04.010
This is also an old tradition

04:04.150 --> 04:05.100
in our bureau.

04:05.790 --> 04:06.760
Don't feel burdened.

04:06.990 --> 04:07.670
Got it.

04:10.230 --> 04:11.350
I think your investigation

04:11.430 --> 04:12.450
is on the right track.

04:12.660 --> 04:13.520
But based on

04:13.550 --> 04:14.800
the files we have now,

04:14.950 --> 04:15.520
there're not many

04:15.550 --> 04:16.550
valuable clues.

04:18.269 --> 04:19.320
Even if we can't find anything,

04:19.470 --> 04:20.750
we have to try.

04:19.829 --> 04:23.440
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

04:21.190 --> 04:22.960
This is what we do, right?

04:23.920 --> 04:25.310
But I always feel like

04:26.110 --> 04:27.000
this case

04:27.030 --> 04:28.070
is somewhat related to

04:28.140 --> 04:28.860
Deng Man's case back then.

04:30.570 --> 04:31.290
Yeah.

04:31.630 --> 04:32.770
This criminal

04:32.909 --> 04:34.960
has been targeting Lu Yan

04:34.990 --> 04:36.050
indirectly or directly

04:36.260 --> 04:38.290
through the deaths of Deng Man, Wang Qianqian and Ding Jing.

04:38.330 --> 04:39.640
I really can't figure out

04:39.909 --> 04:41.290
what his purpose is.

04:42.000 --> 04:42.950
I was thinking,

04:44.550 --> 04:45.430
do you think

04:46.000 --> 04:47.680
this could be meant for me?

04:50.870 --> 04:52.400
But so far,

04:52.470 --> 04:53.280
I haven't found

04:53.310 --> 04:54.640
any clue that could lead to the conclusion that

04:54.670 --> 04:55.760
the crimes he committed were meant for you.

04:56.150 --> 04:57.920
I won't make

04:57.950 --> 04:58.350
such a deduction

04:58.390 --> 04:59.310
before any certain evidence is attained.

05:02.920 --> 05:04.570
So why did he do that?

05:05.070 --> 05:06.420
All right, stop worrying about it.

05:06.510 --> 05:07.680
Go home and have some rest.

05:07.710 --> 05:08.640
Take your mind off it for a bit.

05:09.040 --> 05:09.960
When we find

05:09.990 --> 05:11.780
the real motive for the crimes,

05:11.810 --> 05:12.920
we'll be close to getting the cases solved.

05:13.760 --> 05:20.280
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

05:13.910 --> 05:14.360
Okay.

05:14.630 --> 05:15.110
I'm leaving.

05:15.180 --> 05:15.710
Okay.

05:20.440 --> 05:23.250
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

05:23.910 --> 05:25.080
Peng, I told you

05:25.110 --> 05:26.390
there's no need for you to come.

05:28.830 --> 05:29.860
If I don't come and check on you,

05:29.890 --> 05:31.020
I won't feel assured.

05:32.120 --> 05:33.159
I happen to be free today,

05:33.180 --> 05:34.020
so I'll spend more time with you.

05:35.510 --> 05:37.110
I'm almost recovered.

05:37.590 --> 05:38.320
I only need to stay

05:38.350 --> 05:39.030
a few more days in the hospital

05:39.110 --> 05:40.220
before I can be discharged.

05:40.390 --> 05:41.510
After I'm discharged, get me jobs right away

05:41.550 --> 05:42.620
so I can make money.

05:44.100 --> 05:46.140
You don't actually think the reason why I came to see you

05:46.390 --> 05:47.710
is to get you discharged as soon as possible

05:47.830 --> 05:48.630
so that you can go back to work, do you?

05:49.110 --> 05:50.150
I was only saying that

05:50.230 --> 05:51.430
to show my attitude.

05:52.350 --> 05:53.180
You are so nice to me.

05:53.310 --> 05:53.830
Of course I won't

05:53.870 --> 05:54.830
let our company down.

05:56.830 --> 05:57.630
If all artists

05:57.630 --> 05:58.650
could be like you,

05:58.790 --> 05:59.510
that would be great.

06:02.950 --> 06:04.270
Peng, you're referring to

06:05.860 --> 06:07.270
Liu Keru, right?

06:09.160 --> 06:09.950
How did you know?

06:10.350 --> 06:12.950
I heard something from my assistant.

06:16.090 --> 06:17.480
Peng, there's something

06:17.670 --> 06:19.160
I may not be supposed to say.

06:19.350 --> 06:20.190
I think you should have

06:20.270 --> 06:20.950
punished her long ago.

06:21.270 --> 06:21.990
-Bofeng.
-I...

06:23.150 --> 06:24.430
You're at your prime now.

06:24.480 --> 06:25.110
You must be careful about

06:25.150 --> 06:26.040
everything you say and do.

06:26.460 --> 06:27.750
Don't say anything you shouldn't say

06:27.830 --> 06:29.130
to anyone,

06:29.310 --> 06:30.150
including me.

06:30.350 --> 06:30.750
Well,

06:30.770 --> 06:31.790
I know what you mean.

06:31.830 --> 06:32.830
But you're different

06:32.870 --> 06:33.470
to me.

06:34.710 --> 06:36.150
I treat you as my own brother.

06:36.450 --> 06:37.210
I always tell you everything

06:37.230 --> 06:38.580
about me.

06:40.810 --> 06:41.480
When I say...

06:45.310 --> 06:46.090
Professor Yu.

06:46.350 --> 06:47.270
How are you? Feeling better?

06:48.159 --> 06:49.070
Let me introduce.

06:50.270 --> 06:51.040
This is my boss,

06:51.110 --> 06:51.550
Mr. Wen.

06:51.750 --> 06:52.310
And

06:52.720 --> 06:53.409
this is...

06:53.560 --> 06:54.470
We've met before.

06:54.750 --> 06:56.350
You once came to my company with Jiang Chengyi, right?

06:56.510 --> 06:56.990
Yes.

06:57.280 --> 06:58.650
Sorry for causing you trouble, Professor Yu.

06:59.680 --> 07:00.760
Not at all.

07:01.030 --> 07:02.230
He called me many times

07:02.270 --> 07:04.110
about some interview

07:04.190 --> 07:05.430
that's really urgent, right?

07:06.230 --> 07:07.310
So I brought him books.

07:08.970 --> 07:09.910
I didn't expect

07:10.070 --> 07:11.480
you to work so hard

07:11.510 --> 07:12.590
even in the hospital.

07:14.350 --> 07:15.920
This is a book on criminal psychology.

07:15.990 --> 07:17.490
I highlighted the key points in it.

07:17.670 --> 07:18.960
Complete this exercise book

07:19.000 --> 07:20.510
according to these key points.

07:21.030 --> 07:22.360
After that,

07:22.390 --> 07:24.000
you'll have a grasp

07:24.040 --> 07:25.180
of the basic logic

07:25.270 --> 07:26.000
and professional terms

07:26.030 --> 07:27.350
of criminal psychology.

07:28.390 --> 07:29.170
Do it carefully.

07:29.230 --> 07:30.310
Call me when you're done,

07:30.350 --> 07:31.150
and I'll come collect the homework.

07:31.230 --> 07:31.710
Okay.

07:31.820 --> 07:32.550
Professor Yu

07:32.550 --> 07:33.260
may not know well

07:33.260 --> 07:33.920
about our industry.

07:34.030 --> 07:35.150
In our industry,

07:35.180 --> 07:35.830
urgent matters can't be delayed

07:35.870 --> 07:37.320
even for a second.

07:37.430 --> 07:38.190
But when it's not urgent,

07:38.210 --> 07:39.900
there may be no news

07:39.990 --> 07:41.030
for ten days or even half a month.

07:44.630 --> 07:45.190
Right.

07:45.680 --> 07:46.880
I may not know much

07:46.909 --> 07:47.909
about your industry.

07:48.440 --> 07:49.790
But I believe

07:49.810 --> 07:51.300
it'll be better for artists

07:51.470 --> 07:53.850
to reserve more time to prepare

07:53.990 --> 07:55.150
before they do anything.

07:57.710 --> 07:58.950
You're right, Professor Yu.

08:00.270 --> 08:01.420
Why don't you say thank you?

08:02.350 --> 08:03.470
No need.

08:04.070 --> 08:04.730
You guys continue.

08:05.930 --> 08:06.940
Professor Yu,

08:07.670 --> 08:09.040
why don't you

08:09.100 --> 08:09.900
tutor him now?

08:12.700 --> 08:13.770
I have classes later.

08:14.630 --> 08:15.410
Maybe another day.

08:16.180 --> 08:18.000
I'll text you when I'm done.

08:31.110 --> 08:32.400
The interview is already over.

08:32.830 --> 08:34.350
Why did you ask her to deliver these materials to you?

08:37.900 --> 08:39.190
Didn't you say

08:39.840 --> 08:40.870
you'd tell me everything about you?

08:40.890 --> 08:41.750
Have you forgotten it already?

08:43.640 --> 08:44.320
Well...

08:44.550 --> 08:45.380
Peng.

08:45.400 --> 08:46.840
Actually, I...

08:46.910 --> 08:47.740
You like her?

08:53.570 --> 08:54.160
Yes.

08:56.310 --> 08:56.950
Bofeng.

08:57.850 --> 08:58.970
You should know

08:59.280 --> 09:00.870
our company made you popular

09:00.900 --> 09:01.590
step by step.

09:03.920 --> 09:04.980
I know that.

09:05.870 --> 09:07.940
My plan was to

09:07.960 --> 09:09.930
have a good talk with you after getting discharged.

09:10.110 --> 09:10.750
How would I know

09:10.830 --> 09:11.990
you'd bump into each other today?

09:13.150 --> 09:13.910
Did she agree?

09:15.190 --> 09:15.950
She doesn't know yet.

09:19.000 --> 09:19.800
Make sure you keep me updated on

09:19.840 --> 09:20.870
what you do.

09:22.390 --> 09:23.000
Okay.

09:23.910 --> 09:24.470
Don't worry.

09:24.890 --> 09:26.440
I know what to do.

09:30.510 --> 09:31.760
Every one else in your department had got off work.

09:31.870 --> 09:33.410
Only you, the model worker, was still working.

09:33.630 --> 09:35.080
Dr. Lu, are you off work?

09:35.150 --> 09:35.960
Yeah, I'm off. Bye.

09:35.990 --> 09:36.550
Bye.

09:37.010 --> 09:38.610
What brings you here?

09:38.880 --> 09:40.020
Zhong went to discuss business,

09:40.070 --> 09:41.130
and I was left alone at home.

09:41.230 --> 09:41.710
I thought I'd come

09:41.710 --> 09:43.550
to ask the baby's godmother to buy me dinner.

09:43.780 --> 09:45.350
Is he out making money for baby formula?

09:45.370 --> 09:47.530
I don't expect him to make much money.

09:47.590 --> 09:48.430
As long as our family is safe

09:48.470 --> 09:50.170
and healthy.

09:51.070 --> 09:52.570
What about your boyfriend?

09:52.750 --> 09:54.110
He went to see his parents.

09:54.870 --> 09:55.910
Little baby.

09:56.000 --> 09:56.950
Godmother will cook for you,

09:56.970 --> 09:57.880
okay?

09:58.340 --> 09:59.750
Why bother cooking?

09:59.780 --> 10:01.460
Let's just eat outside.

10:01.550 --> 10:03.060
You can't eat outside now.

10:03.150 --> 10:04.230
The oil they use is not clean.

10:04.300 --> 10:05.380
I'll cook for you.

10:05.990 --> 10:07.590
We can talk about it again in six months.

10:08.580 --> 10:09.520
Hello, Zhong.

10:10.100 --> 10:11.240
Don't have dinner yet.

10:11.260 --> 10:12.620
We may need to have dinner with our clients.

10:13.470 --> 10:14.150
Okay.

10:14.170 --> 10:15.390
See you in the office in a bit.

10:22.790 --> 10:23.500
Still haven't finished?

10:24.690 --> 10:25.480
I don't know how to do it.

10:25.540 --> 10:26.110
What kind of question is this?

10:26.130 --> 10:27.510
There's no logic at all.

10:28.280 --> 10:28.940
What question is it?

10:28.980 --> 10:30.260
Look at this question, Peng.

10:31.680 --> 10:33.160
It says a pair of sisters

10:33.200 --> 10:34.670
saw a man

10:34.670 --> 10:35.770
on their father's funeral,

10:35.830 --> 10:36.760
and they fell in love with him at the same time.

10:36.790 --> 10:37.760
The next day,

10:37.790 --> 10:38.990
the younger sister killed the older sister.

10:39.180 --> 10:39.670
The question is,

10:39.700 --> 10:41.540
what's the younger sister's motive for murder?

10:43.800 --> 10:45.050
Isn't it easy?

10:45.940 --> 10:47.660
The younger sister wants to hold another funeral

10:47.910 --> 10:49.140
so that she can see that man again.

10:50.280 --> 10:51.790
Peng, you do have a point.

10:53.850 --> 10:55.270
You've learned this too?

10:55.960 --> 10:57.670
You're amazing, Peng.

10:57.910 --> 10:58.480
All right.

10:58.510 --> 10:59.470
Just do your homework.

11:00.440 --> 11:01.380
But Bofeng,

11:01.520 --> 11:03.060
don't blame me for not reminding you.

11:03.710 --> 11:05.090
After you lie once,

11:05.190 --> 11:06.060
you'll have to make up thousands of lies

11:06.110 --> 11:07.070
to patch up that lie.

11:07.750 --> 11:09.230
But I have no choice.

11:09.260 --> 11:10.260
I'm cornered.

11:11.280 --> 11:12.930
You must be the first person

11:12.950 --> 11:14.130
to pursue a girl this way.

11:14.510 --> 11:15.450
Good luck.

11:15.470 --> 11:16.180
See you.

11:27.590 --> 11:28.190
Come on.

11:28.210 --> 11:28.730
Come on.

11:29.050 --> 11:30.370
Try it and see if it's too salty or too bland.

11:34.060 --> 11:34.790
It's perfectly cooked.

11:34.940 --> 11:35.560
Really?

11:35.580 --> 11:36.420
Your cooking is excellent.

11:36.450 --> 11:37.720
My dad's cooking is indeed the best.

11:37.830 --> 11:38.790
-Of course.
-Yeah.

11:40.950 --> 11:41.510
Well...

11:41.530 --> 11:42.760
Dad, Mom.

11:44.490 --> 11:45.850
Are you free

11:46.120 --> 11:46.790
next weekend?

11:47.030 --> 11:47.690
What?

11:47.720 --> 11:49.050
Are you bringing your girlfriend back?

11:56.690 --> 11:57.850
Really?

11:57.880 --> 11:58.520
Yes.

11:59.710 --> 12:00.740
Is it Dr. Lu?

12:03.140 --> 12:03.780
Yes.

12:06.220 --> 12:07.190
My goodness, Son.

12:07.190 --> 12:07.920
Thumbs-up for you.

12:07.950 --> 12:08.910
You're awesome.

12:09.270 --> 12:11.440
You really got her to be your girlfriend?

12:11.470 --> 12:12.970
Who does our son take after? So nice.

12:13.010 --> 12:13.610
Son.

12:13.970 --> 12:14.840
Are you sure about this?

12:15.890 --> 12:16.620
Yes.

12:17.550 --> 12:19.000
Then make sure you

12:19.030 --> 12:20.230
make it clear to Dr. Lu that

12:20.440 --> 12:21.680
you'll be in the front line

12:21.710 --> 12:22.810
for the rest of your life.

12:23.000 --> 12:23.870
I'm worried

12:23.890 --> 12:25.060
she'll be frightened and worried all the time

12:25.250 --> 12:27.010
in the future like your mother.

12:27.590 --> 12:28.150
But

12:28.170 --> 12:29.890
I definitely support you.

12:30.060 --> 12:30.800
But Son,

12:31.190 --> 12:31.950
you must

12:32.200 --> 12:34.670
listen to Dr. Lu more.

12:35.430 --> 12:36.030
Okay.

12:36.030 --> 12:37.790
She knows

12:37.830 --> 12:39.040
the situation and nature

12:39.310 --> 12:40.270
of my work.

12:40.580 --> 12:42.550
And we've been together for a while.

12:42.790 --> 12:43.430
She can accept it.

12:43.670 --> 12:45.230
Okay, that's good.

12:45.230 --> 12:46.700
I knew Dr. Lu

12:46.750 --> 12:48.360
was a sensible girl.

12:48.380 --> 12:49.480
Besides,

12:49.630 --> 12:50.710
when you choose someone,

12:50.730 --> 12:51.390
right?

12:51.420 --> 12:53.100
You should support

12:53.190 --> 12:54.180
and respect each other.

12:54.390 --> 12:54.790
Right?

12:54.840 --> 12:56.160
Besides,

12:56.270 --> 12:57.590
if you weren't a policeman back then,

12:57.670 --> 12:58.310
being all upright and cool,

12:58.330 --> 12:59.390
would I have fallen for you?

12:59.470 --> 13:00.230
If it weren't for that police uniform,

13:00.230 --> 13:01.110
I might not have married you.

13:01.110 --> 13:02.660
That's true. I did look great in the police uniform.

13:02.830 --> 13:03.480
Exactly.

13:03.550 --> 13:05.280
The point is you loved my cooking.

13:06.430 --> 13:07.800
That was just a bonus.

13:10.130 --> 13:11.760
Let's make it

13:12.110 --> 13:12.910
next Sunday then.

13:13.670 --> 13:14.410
It's a deal.

13:14.830 --> 13:15.270
Okay.

13:15.320 --> 13:16.080
Alright then.

13:16.100 --> 13:17.220
I'll call Xu

13:17.250 --> 13:18.050
right away

13:18.230 --> 13:20.520
and ask him to save

13:20.670 --> 13:21.370
some high-quality pork butt for me.

13:21.430 --> 13:22.070
Okay.

13:22.140 --> 13:23.890
Make your specialties.

13:23.950 --> 13:24.950
Finish your meal first. No hurry.

13:27.200 --> 13:28.200
Tell me, Son,

13:28.430 --> 13:29.720
where are you two at in your relationship?

13:31.150 --> 13:31.750
Well...

13:32.110 --> 13:33.470
We're just dating normally.

13:34.020 --> 13:36.190
When pursuing a girl, you need to make hay while the sun shines.

13:36.400 --> 13:37.760
You must treat her well,

13:37.790 --> 13:38.450
understand?

13:38.470 --> 13:39.410
I do. I know.

13:39.460 --> 13:40.510
If you don't know how, ask your dad to teach you.

13:41.310 --> 13:42.270
The time when my dad was dating...

13:42.860 --> 13:43.770
It was in the last century.

13:43.830 --> 13:44.710
Learn to cook from him.

13:44.790 --> 13:46.230
I can't use his tricks.

13:48.230 --> 13:49.000
How nice.

13:49.040 --> 13:51.820
[Huiting Complex]

13:52.170 --> 13:52.840
Try it.

13:54.340 --> 13:55.180
Is it good?

13:56.720 --> 13:57.960
Really good.

13:58.070 --> 13:58.630
Not lying?

13:58.710 --> 13:59.810
I'm not.

14:00.670 --> 14:01.190
You know what?

14:01.230 --> 14:02.670
Jiang Chengyi has been cooking here

14:02.730 --> 14:04.320
and showing off his cooking skills,

14:04.350 --> 14:05.100
you know?

14:05.150 --> 14:06.970
I have to learn some specialties

14:07.030 --> 14:08.950
and take him down with a single brilliant feat.

14:10.780 --> 14:11.550
I support you.

14:11.630 --> 14:12.430
I'm blessed.

14:13.310 --> 14:14.460
You just said

14:14.790 --> 14:16.550
you didn't think it was a good idea

14:16.550 --> 14:18.780
for Zhong to do business with Wen Peng. Why is that?

14:21.500 --> 14:22.990
Well, as for Senior Wen,

14:23.020 --> 14:25.150
he does have good resources and connections.

14:25.310 --> 14:26.350
After all,

14:26.390 --> 14:27.550
he's been in the industry for so many years.

14:27.910 --> 14:29.550
But Zhong

14:29.670 --> 14:30.430
has always been focusing his energy

14:30.460 --> 14:31.610
on me.

14:31.670 --> 14:33.100
He never cared much about his career,

14:33.270 --> 14:35.110
and he's honest and naive.

14:35.270 --> 14:36.240
I'm worried he'll suffer losses.

14:39.060 --> 14:40.870
It's understandable that you have concerns.

14:40.950 --> 14:41.830
But

14:42.710 --> 14:43.910
I feel that

14:44.190 --> 14:46.520
Senior Wen is not that kind of person.

14:48.190 --> 14:49.070
You feel?

14:49.520 --> 14:51.400
Do you think what you feel is correct?

14:52.630 --> 14:53.760
Haven't you noticed that

14:53.830 --> 14:54.630
Senior Wen Peng

14:54.670 --> 14:55.910
treats you a bit differently?

14:56.950 --> 14:58.960
Are you kidding me,

14:58.980 --> 14:59.930
Sis?

14:59.960 --> 15:01.670
Senior Wen and I...

15:01.800 --> 15:03.800
We are just senior and junior fellows.

15:04.790 --> 15:06.230
You treat him as your senior,

15:06.270 --> 15:07.280
but he may not

15:07.310 --> 15:08.720
think the same about you.

15:09.470 --> 15:10.750
Think about it.

15:11.080 --> 15:12.950
He's a man who never married

15:13.240 --> 15:14.100
or dated

15:14.130 --> 15:15.000
in the past eight years.

15:15.110 --> 15:16.250
He's always so distant,

15:16.280 --> 15:17.340
but he only takes

15:17.390 --> 15:18.750
attentive care of you.

15:20.790 --> 15:22.050
If you weren't pregnant…

15:22.110 --> 15:22.900
I wouldn't hit a pregnant woman.

15:22.930 --> 15:24.100
Listen.

15:24.310 --> 15:25.350
That's not possible.

15:27.510 --> 15:29.100
Attentive care?

15:29.750 --> 15:30.830
You must be kidding.

15:32.230 --> 15:33.310
Think about it yourself.

15:43.630 --> 15:44.330
Peng.

15:44.550 --> 15:46.000
Is Mr. Ke coming or not?

15:47.950 --> 15:48.440
Exactly.

15:48.480 --> 15:49.690
It's been three hours.

15:49.910 --> 15:50.510
What's the rush?

15:51.110 --> 15:52.110
He owns the IP.

15:52.190 --> 15:53.360
Do you know how many people are fighting for it?

15:53.830 --> 15:55.270
Of course he makes the call.

15:57.240 --> 15:57.910
Mr. Wen.

15:57.930 --> 15:58.940
Mr. Ke is here.

16:01.300 --> 16:02.180
Hello, Peng.

16:02.350 --> 16:02.950
Hello, Mr. Ke.

16:03.590 --> 16:04.750
Bring me the tea

16:04.770 --> 16:05.400
I bought a few days ago.

16:05.650 --> 16:06.220
Okay.

16:06.380 --> 16:07.290
Sorry to keep you waiting.

16:07.790 --> 16:08.880
We've also just finished our work.

16:10.190 --> 16:10.820
Mr. Ke.

16:10.840 --> 16:11.680
Let me introduce.

16:12.250 --> 16:12.990
Zhong Wenxuan.

16:13.030 --> 16:13.630
Yuan Dalu.

16:13.920 --> 16:15.230
They were both my classmates in college,

16:15.250 --> 16:16.400
and my partners now.

16:16.450 --> 16:17.560
They also work in the film and television industry.

16:18.790 --> 16:19.720
Hello, Mr. Ke.

16:19.800 --> 16:20.640
I'll skip the tea.

16:20.660 --> 16:21.540
Time is limited.

16:21.560 --> 16:22.860
Let's make it short.

16:22.900 --> 16:23.340
Sit.

16:23.460 --> 16:24.270
Come on, let's sit and talk.

16:25.000 --> 16:25.710
Sit.

16:30.470 --> 16:31.180
Mr. Ke.

16:31.500 --> 16:32.940
I've gone through

16:32.960 --> 16:33.650
the project proposal and the creative team.

16:33.670 --> 16:34.560
There's no problem with that.

16:34.810 --> 16:35.910
The script is also very good.

16:36.110 --> 16:36.990
It suits

16:37.010 --> 16:38.570
the trending feminist theme very well.

16:38.990 --> 16:40.280
And of course, thank you very much

16:40.310 --> 16:41.470
for letting Bofeng be a part of it.

16:41.840 --> 16:42.620
That's what I should do.

16:42.660 --> 16:44.550
Bofeng is an excellent actor.

16:45.670 --> 16:47.120
After all, as you know,

16:47.150 --> 16:48.550
we have many choices.

16:48.910 --> 16:50.350
We own a big IP.

16:50.710 --> 16:52.470
Luckily, you were willing to make an advance payment,

16:52.490 --> 16:53.770
which solved some problems for us.

16:54.650 --> 16:55.820
So, Mr. Ke,

16:55.850 --> 16:56.880
the reason why I wanted to see you

16:56.960 --> 16:57.900
is to tell you that

16:58.310 --> 17:00.070
I want to give some of my investment shares

17:00.150 --> 17:01.070
to my friends.

17:02.460 --> 17:03.300
To them?

17:06.079 --> 17:06.819
Please don't get me wrong.

17:07.140 --> 17:08.339
What I mean is,

17:08.470 --> 17:09.569
I'll give my part

17:09.630 --> 17:10.480
to them.

17:10.550 --> 17:11.390
I won't take any of your share.

17:11.890 --> 17:13.829
After all, you are in charge here.

17:13.950 --> 17:14.990
I have to keep you informed.

17:17.790 --> 17:18.810
Peng.

17:19.230 --> 17:20.450
Why would you want to do that?

17:20.710 --> 17:22.290
This is a project with promising profit.

17:22.390 --> 17:23.230
Why would you give the profit

17:23.270 --> 17:24.310
to some other people just like that?

17:25.660 --> 17:26.859
They're my friends.

17:27.230 --> 17:28.160
Please give us younger generation

17:28.190 --> 17:28.870
some opportunities.

17:29.150 --> 17:29.780
Right.

17:29.780 --> 17:31.510
Mr. Ke, please help us.

17:33.590 --> 17:34.570
Peng.

17:34.630 --> 17:35.660
You should know

17:35.950 --> 17:37.040
the only reason why you

17:37.070 --> 17:38.030
got to be part of this

17:38.280 --> 17:39.110
is that

17:39.110 --> 17:40.910
you let me use Yu Bofeng for free.

17:41.430 --> 17:42.730
Mr. Ke, sorry

17:42.990 --> 17:44.390
to interrupt.

17:44.720 --> 17:45.600
Peng and I

17:45.630 --> 17:46.510
were college classmates.

17:46.760 --> 17:48.460
I trust him, and he trusts me.

17:48.750 --> 17:49.350
In business,

17:49.390 --> 17:50.830
what matters is credibility.

17:51.380 --> 17:52.270
Since he treats me well,

17:52.270 --> 17:53.110
I'll definitely

17:53.150 --> 17:54.300
repay him twice as much in the future.

17:55.320 --> 17:56.880
We may be inexperienced,

17:57.190 --> 17:58.670
but we won't let you down.

17:58.990 --> 17:59.790
Don't worry.

18:00.500 --> 18:02.670
But if you really can't approve of it,

18:03.380 --> 18:04.880
we won't make things difficult for Peng.

18:04.900 --> 18:05.780
No, Mr. Ke.

18:05.920 --> 18:06.640
What Zhong meant is that…

18:06.660 --> 18:07.220
Mr. Ke.

18:07.540 --> 18:08.200
Here's the thing.

18:08.590 --> 18:09.870
This friend of mine

18:09.890 --> 18:11.110
is an honest and simple man.

18:11.570 --> 18:12.580
He's not very eloquent,

18:13.500 --> 18:14.260
but

18:14.300 --> 18:16.060
he's very reliable in work and life.

18:16.130 --> 18:16.870
So,

18:17.110 --> 18:17.830
you can count on him.

18:19.100 --> 18:19.780
Yes.

18:19.810 --> 18:20.560
Mr. Ke.

18:20.640 --> 18:22.180
Please give us a chance.

18:27.370 --> 18:28.290
Zhong, right?

18:30.130 --> 18:31.430
I really like

18:31.430 --> 18:32.990
your straightforward personality.

18:34.040 --> 18:34.990
To be honest,

18:35.010 --> 18:35.900
I only trust him

18:36.200 --> 18:37.160
in this project.

18:37.550 --> 18:38.710
Since he trusts you,

18:39.480 --> 18:40.380
let's

18:41.160 --> 18:42.290
work together and give it a try.

18:44.740 --> 18:45.550
That's great, Mr. Ke.

18:45.580 --> 18:46.350
Thank you.

18:48.080 --> 18:48.680
Mr. Ke.

18:50.070 --> 18:51.110
We look forward to working with you.

18:51.850 --> 18:52.920
Draft

18:52.960 --> 18:53.640
a cooperation agreement

18:53.670 --> 18:54.470
and send it to me,

18:54.500 --> 18:55.300
and we'll talk later.

18:55.990 --> 18:56.500
Okay.

18:56.830 --> 18:57.440
Thank you, Mr. Ke.

18:57.470 --> 18:58.030
Thank you, Mr. Ke.

18:58.180 --> 18:59.000
It's getting late.

18:59.020 --> 19:00.200
I have to go.

19:00.220 --> 19:01.110
You guys continue.

19:01.640 --> 19:02.280
See you.

19:07.060 --> 19:07.780
Mr. Ke.

19:12.720 --> 19:14.210
I've got the club ready for you.

19:14.240 --> 19:15.470
You can go right away.

19:15.670 --> 19:16.230
All right.

19:16.800 --> 19:17.490
Thank you.

19:25.350 --> 19:25.990
What?

19:26.350 --> 19:27.190
Do you feel uncomfortable about it?

19:31.470 --> 19:32.230
What's the point

19:32.260 --> 19:33.140
of talking business like this?

19:33.850 --> 19:35.330
You look like you've eaten fly poop.

19:36.950 --> 19:38.560
I'm already used to it.

19:39.790 --> 19:40.830
Look how tactful

19:40.880 --> 19:41.550
Dalu is.

19:42.710 --> 19:43.640
You should learn

19:43.670 --> 19:44.350
from him in this regard.

19:47.580 --> 19:48.300
Zhong.

19:49.030 --> 19:50.410
You are a businessman now,

19:50.750 --> 19:51.910
not a moral model.

19:52.910 --> 19:54.270
If you don't like it,

19:54.430 --> 19:55.610
you can quit.

19:55.890 --> 19:56.950
To make money,

19:57.350 --> 19:59.050
sometimes you have to kneel,

19:59.080 --> 20:01.830
and sometimes you have to play dumb.

20:02.350 --> 20:03.030
As long as it's not against the law,

20:03.070 --> 20:03.870
right?

20:10.160 --> 20:10.980
It's getting late.

20:11.510 --> 20:12.340
Go home now.

20:12.440 --> 20:14.040
Have Keru comfort you,

20:14.110 --> 20:14.860
and you'll be fine.

20:15.550 --> 20:16.310
Alright, Peng.

20:16.670 --> 20:17.650
No matter what,

20:18.110 --> 20:18.870
thank you for today.

20:20.830 --> 20:21.570
Well,

20:21.750 --> 20:22.730
let me treat you to a meal.

20:23.030 --> 20:23.430
Right.

20:23.450 --> 20:25.290
The contract is almost settled.

20:25.350 --> 20:25.950
Let's have dinner together.

20:26.080 --> 20:27.320
I'll take you home after dinner.

20:27.790 --> 20:28.310
No need.

20:28.400 --> 20:29.790
I still have things to do.

20:29.820 --> 20:31.060
You guys go back first.

20:33.400 --> 20:34.050
Another day then.

20:35.590 --> 20:36.940
We're off then.

20:43.510 --> 20:44.030
Zhong.

20:44.120 --> 20:46.040
Do you think we can trust Mr. Ke?

20:47.500 --> 20:48.950
I don't know whether we can trust him or not,

20:49.470 --> 20:50.630
but I don't like

20:50.670 --> 20:51.710
the way he deals with things.

20:53.390 --> 20:54.030
That's true.

20:54.640 --> 20:55.440
We've been

20:55.480 --> 20:56.190
in this industry

20:56.230 --> 20:57.200
for so many years.

20:57.230 --> 20:58.870
We've seen all kinds of bosses.

20:59.270 --> 21:01.090
Most of them are modest and cautious.

21:01.110 --> 21:02.460
There are not many people

21:02.550 --> 21:03.190
like him.

21:03.210 --> 21:03.820
By the way,

21:03.840 --> 21:04.890
he even asked artists to have a drink with him.

21:04.990 --> 21:05.910
I'm speechless.

21:08.910 --> 21:10.770
Maybe people are just different.

21:10.790 --> 21:11.630
Peng is right.

21:12.030 --> 21:13.230
We are doing business now.

21:13.250 --> 21:14.290
We need to be flexible.

21:15.270 --> 21:16.620
As long as we don't get involved

21:16.790 --> 21:18.300
in anything that's against the law.

21:19.260 --> 21:20.200
Of course.

21:20.610 --> 21:22.090
Peng only did it to help us.

21:22.120 --> 21:23.610
We can't embarrass him.

21:57.950 --> 21:59.060
You're back, Honey.

21:59.080 --> 21:59.880
You're still up, Honey.

22:00.680 --> 22:01.450
How was it?

22:01.790 --> 22:02.510
Did it go well?

22:08.450 --> 22:10.040
Kind of.

22:11.360 --> 22:12.850
Why do you look unhappy then?

22:14.840 --> 22:17.300
Maybe I haven't socialized for too long.

22:18.000 --> 22:19.080
I feel a bit uncomfortable with it.

22:20.900 --> 22:22.370
If you feel uncomfortable,

22:22.400 --> 22:23.510
just quit.

22:24.030 --> 22:24.670
Anyway, I think

22:24.690 --> 22:25.750
our family is doing well now.

22:25.770 --> 22:26.780
We have enough money to spend.

22:28.030 --> 22:29.370
Don't worry, Honey.

22:29.800 --> 22:31.540
Peng and I have been working together for so many years.

22:31.910 --> 22:33.310
His company is big,

22:33.470 --> 22:35.110
and it has a great reputation in the industry.

22:35.910 --> 22:36.440
Today,

22:36.470 --> 22:37.470
he introduced a boss to me,

22:37.650 --> 22:39.580
saying there's a project of a big IP.

22:40.110 --> 22:41.170
I only need to co-invest with him.

22:41.230 --> 22:42.290
It's secured profit.

22:43.470 --> 22:44.330
Besides,

22:44.510 --> 22:45.200
making movies

22:45.230 --> 22:46.470
has always been my dream, right?

22:47.030 --> 22:48.600
And you're always supportive of me.

22:48.840 --> 22:50.920
Of course I support you.

22:50.940 --> 22:51.710
I'm just worried that you'll be too tired.

22:52.710 --> 22:53.750
I'm not tired.

22:53.780 --> 22:55.660
You are the most tired one in our family now.

22:56.600 --> 22:58.090
You're pregnant.

22:58.710 --> 23:00.790
I'll take care of our family from now on.

23:01.080 --> 23:03.190
All you need to do is take good care of your health.

23:04.300 --> 23:05.110
Let's sleep.

23:10.030 --> 23:10.710
I'm hungry.

23:12.630 --> 23:13.270
Oh?

23:13.720 --> 23:15.600
Pregnant women get hungry easily, right?

23:15.900 --> 23:17.200
What do you want to eat? I'll cook it for you.

23:18.510 --> 23:19.680
Instant noodles.

23:20.800 --> 23:21.810
You want eggs?

23:22.190 --> 23:23.260
Yes, I want two.

23:23.390 --> 23:24.230
Okay.

23:25.800 --> 23:27.060
Wait here, Honey.

23:27.750 --> 23:28.870
Call me when you're done.

23:29.230 --> 23:30.990
I'll serve it to bed for you,

23:31.020 --> 23:31.540
okay?

23:35.050 --> 23:35.720
So sweet.

23:39.030 --> 23:39.630
How is it?

23:40.310 --> 23:40.910
It's good.

23:42.870 --> 23:44.360
So, we'll go to my parents' house

23:44.750 --> 23:45.590
this weekend.

23:47.150 --> 23:47.750
Okay.

23:50.390 --> 23:51.110
Are you nervous?

23:52.550 --> 23:53.390
Why should I be nervous?

23:53.550 --> 23:55.070
It's not like I haven't seen them before.

23:55.630 --> 23:56.790
And I already told my mom that

23:56.810 --> 23:57.780
I'd go to your parents' house for dinner.

24:00.260 --> 24:01.230
What did your mom say?

24:02.780 --> 24:04.490
Nothing.

24:04.510 --> 24:06.260
She just complained that I told her about it too late

24:06.310 --> 24:08.210
and I dated behind her back.

24:11.030 --> 24:11.750
She's right, actually.

24:12.150 --> 24:13.070
Do you not want to

24:13.070 --> 24:14.030
introduce me to your mom?

24:15.720 --> 24:16.840
I just haven't found

24:16.870 --> 24:18.060
the right opportunity.

24:19.490 --> 24:20.170
Eat up.

24:26.730 --> 24:28.080
I applied to the bureau

24:29.510 --> 24:30.510
to retrieve and re-investigate

24:30.870 --> 24:31.960
some details

24:31.990 --> 24:32.750
of Deng Man's case.

24:33.750 --> 24:35.240
I always feel her case must

24:35.510 --> 24:37.470
have something to do with these recent cases,

24:38.530 --> 24:40.270
but I haven't found any pattern.

24:41.990 --> 24:42.680
Really?

24:45.560 --> 24:46.600
If I don't

24:46.630 --> 24:47.550
figure these out,

24:48.980 --> 24:50.170
I can't sleep tight at night.

24:51.750 --> 24:52.510
That's great.

24:52.950 --> 24:53.870
Thank you.

24:55.940 --> 24:57.230
It's to serve the people.

25:15.350 --> 25:15.990
Jiang.

25:16.030 --> 25:17.260
What are you doing?

25:17.350 --> 25:18.670
The kids are almost here.

25:18.710 --> 25:19.940
The house isn't tidied up yet.

25:20.030 --> 25:21.150
Why are you still dawdling inside...

25:23.470 --> 25:24.340
Am I handsome?

25:25.090 --> 25:26.100
What are you doing?

25:26.450 --> 25:27.520
Dress up to see my daughter-in-law.

25:28.350 --> 25:29.600
Why don't you just

25:29.670 --> 25:30.720
put on your police uniform then?

25:30.750 --> 25:31.190
You...

25:31.240 --> 25:32.240
I did try to put it on,

25:32.270 --> 25:32.910
but my belly is too big

25:32.940 --> 25:33.680
and I can't fit in.

25:33.750 --> 25:35.390
Otherwise, I would have put on

25:35.430 --> 25:36.190
my summer uniform, okay?

25:36.210 --> 25:37.820
That's much cooler than this.

25:37.850 --> 25:39.970
Give you an inch, and you'll take a mile.

25:40.030 --> 25:41.030
Are you meeting your daughter-in-law

25:41.050 --> 25:42.290
or interrogating a criminal?

25:42.320 --> 25:43.970
I do have to interrogate her.

25:44.040 --> 25:44.810
Right?

25:45.760 --> 25:46.800
What a crook.

25:46.840 --> 25:47.270
Seriously.

25:47.270 --> 25:48.320
Take it off.

25:48.430 --> 25:50.040
-It's not appropriate.
-What should I wear then?

25:50.110 --> 25:51.200
You need to make her feel at home.

25:51.220 --> 25:52.110
Just wear what you usually wear

25:52.130 --> 25:52.930
at home.

25:52.990 --> 25:54.450
W-What do I normally wear at home?

25:54.630 --> 25:55.310
Loungewear, of course.

25:55.310 --> 25:56.550
I bought so many sets for you.

25:56.580 --> 25:57.790
Take it off. Hurry up.

25:57.870 --> 25:58.470
Why do I feel

25:58.580 --> 25:59.730
quite nervous?

25:59.970 --> 26:00.820
Take these off.

26:00.950 --> 26:01.870
Alright. Alright.

26:02.180 --> 26:03.670
Why should you be nervous?

26:03.870 --> 26:04.470
Right?

26:04.490 --> 26:05.530
You need to relax

26:05.560 --> 26:07.270
and make her feel at home.

26:07.330 --> 26:08.890
If you're nervous, she'll be tense too.

26:08.920 --> 26:09.480
Right. Right.

26:09.510 --> 26:09.790
Right?

26:09.790 --> 26:11.430
Our family atmosphere is not like that.

26:13.150 --> 26:13.620
Come on.

26:14.380 --> 26:15.280
Dad.

26:15.840 --> 26:17.140
They're back.

26:17.190 --> 26:18.220
Take it off.

26:18.250 --> 26:19.180
Don't embarrass me.

26:19.200 --> 26:20.710
Coming.

26:20.870 --> 26:22.240
Jiang, hurry up.

26:22.390 --> 26:23.150
Okay. Okay.

26:23.190 --> 26:24.740
Which outfit should I wear?

26:26.130 --> 26:26.880
You're back.

26:26.920 --> 26:27.970
Whatever. This is it.

26:29.280 --> 26:30.300
Yan, you're here.

26:30.320 --> 26:30.910
Auntie.

26:30.990 --> 26:31.550
Come on.

26:31.830 --> 26:32.920
Uncle.

26:34.220 --> 26:35.260
You're dressed quite formally.

26:35.350 --> 26:35.870
-Yeah.
-Well…

26:35.890 --> 26:36.810
We have a guest.

26:36.910 --> 26:37.600
Well...

26:38.510 --> 26:39.130
Come on in.

26:39.230 --> 26:39.750
Come on.

26:39.870 --> 26:41.070
Come in and have a seat, Yan.

26:41.510 --> 26:42.550
Come on.

26:42.620 --> 26:43.910
Come on.

26:47.170 --> 26:47.960
Here, Uncle.

26:47.980 --> 26:49.380
This wine is for you.

26:50.350 --> 26:51.110
You really have great taste.

26:51.130 --> 26:52.230
I love this wine.

26:52.250 --> 26:52.990
He's so happy.

26:53.080 --> 26:53.750
Auntie.

26:53.770 --> 26:54.930
I bought you a scarf.

26:55.520 --> 26:56.770
You're too polite.

26:56.830 --> 26:57.750
Here, have some fruits.

26:57.770 --> 26:59.000
We specially went to buy it.

26:59.070 --> 26:59.950
Really?

27:00.500 --> 27:02.060
It's getting cold.

27:02.190 --> 27:03.490
I can put it on soon.

27:03.630 --> 27:04.390
Thank you, Yan.

27:04.390 --> 27:05.230
It's nothing.

27:06.950 --> 27:07.830
The kids are already here.

27:07.830 --> 27:09.000
Go on and cook.

27:09.430 --> 27:10.350
-Okay.
-I'll go help.

27:10.370 --> 27:10.870
No need.

27:11.080 --> 27:12.710
The Jiang's family rule is that

27:12.950 --> 27:14.070
men are in charge of cooking,

27:14.090 --> 27:15.330
and women only need to wait to eat.

27:15.930 --> 27:16.510
Come help me.

27:16.510 --> 27:17.150
But, Dad,

27:17.870 --> 27:18.910
are you going to cook in this?

27:19.070 --> 27:20.610
If I hadn't stopped him today,

27:20.660 --> 27:22.540
your dad would have put on his police uniform.

27:22.670 --> 27:24.030
He only gave up because his belly was too big

27:24.030 --> 27:25.470
and he couldn't button it. And...

27:25.490 --> 27:26.620
Who said I have a big belly?

27:27.240 --> 27:27.830
Okay, let's go.

27:27.860 --> 27:28.730
Okay, let's go.

27:28.770 --> 27:29.290
Come help me.

27:29.310 --> 27:30.480
Making it so grand.

27:31.150 --> 27:32.090
Sit tight.

27:32.240 --> 27:34.120
Even a great chef wouldn't dress like this.

27:35.100 --> 27:37.130
Just stay seated.

27:37.190 --> 27:38.200
Our family rule is

27:38.230 --> 27:39.820
men are in charge of cooking.

27:39.950 --> 27:41.220
Have your uncle cook

27:41.270 --> 27:42.110
his specialty...

27:42.190 --> 27:43.110
Stir-fried Beef.

27:44.220 --> 27:45.750
Chengyi made it for you before?

27:46.930 --> 27:47.780
It's very delicious.

27:48.310 --> 27:49.340
That's more like it.

27:49.360 --> 27:50.540
That's what a good guy should do.

27:52.290 --> 27:53.060
Since we have nothing to do for now,

27:53.060 --> 27:54.030
how about I take you

27:54.110 --> 27:55.080
on a room tour?

27:55.400 --> 27:55.990
Sure.

27:56.020 --> 27:57.210
Let's go.

27:58.780 --> 27:59.630
This used to be

27:59.830 --> 28:02.140
Chengyi's room.

28:02.220 --> 28:04.010
We've renovated it into a study.

28:04.040 --> 28:06.030
These are all his awards certificates.

28:07.350 --> 28:07.830
Look.

28:08.140 --> 28:09.940
Bachelor's degree certificate.

28:11.370 --> 28:12.960
Energetic young man.

28:17.770 --> 28:18.430
This is his

28:18.430 --> 28:19.650
third-class merit medal.

28:21.680 --> 28:23.430
He risked his life for it.

28:25.160 --> 28:26.340
His father and I

28:26.540 --> 28:27.980
have worried about him a lot.

28:28.270 --> 28:28.750
Here.

28:31.940 --> 28:32.800
This one.

28:33.950 --> 28:34.550
Look.

28:35.190 --> 28:36.270
Back in college,

28:36.290 --> 28:37.610
he was in the basketball team.

28:37.750 --> 28:39.110
Look at these brats,

28:39.130 --> 28:40.580
reeking with sweat all day.

28:41.570 --> 28:42.760
They were really happy.

28:44.280 --> 28:45.010
By the way,

28:49.510 --> 28:50.150
Yan, come here.

28:54.170 --> 28:55.780
This is Chengyi's childhood album.

28:57.180 --> 28:58.740
This is when he was three years old.

28:58.830 --> 29:00.240
He was very shy back then.

29:00.270 --> 29:01.750
His dad was even worried that

29:01.790 --> 29:02.620
he'd suffer autism.

29:04.550 --> 29:05.190
Look.

29:07.520 --> 29:08.790
This is when he was ten years old.

29:09.200 --> 29:11.410
He already wanted to be a police officer at that time.

29:11.480 --> 29:12.470
As soon as his dad came home,

29:12.550 --> 29:13.900
he'd snatch his dad's cap, put it on,

29:14.000 --> 29:14.750
and go to the courtyard

29:14.750 --> 29:15.830
to show it off.

29:15.870 --> 29:16.620
You know what?

29:16.710 --> 29:18.380
All the children in the neighborhood

29:18.410 --> 29:19.000
were disciplined by him so well that

29:19.060 --> 29:20.410
they'd salute him when they saw him.

29:21.150 --> 29:22.230
He was a king of kids.

29:29.340 --> 29:30.580
In fact, Chengyi

29:31.530 --> 29:33.150
may seem carefree,

29:33.800 --> 29:34.880
but deep within,

29:35.160 --> 29:36.880
he's very

29:39.860 --> 29:42.850
sensitive and fragile.

29:47.920 --> 29:49.560
I guess he didn't tell you this,

29:50.550 --> 29:51.510
but actually,

29:52.120 --> 29:53.890
when he was in college,

29:54.270 --> 29:55.830
he dated once.

29:57.640 --> 29:58.880
And they broke up

29:58.910 --> 30:00.190
for some unknown reason.

30:01.760 --> 30:03.240
His father and I didn't dare to ask.

30:03.470 --> 30:05.160
He'd get angry with us whenever we asked.

30:05.550 --> 30:06.430
All these years, he's locked himself

30:06.460 --> 30:07.480
in the police force.

30:07.590 --> 30:08.590
He seldom came back.

30:08.590 --> 30:10.030
Every time he was back, he'd have injuries all over his body.

30:12.180 --> 30:12.870
Yan.

30:13.800 --> 30:15.460
I just feel that

30:16.170 --> 30:17.280
you are like

30:17.310 --> 30:18.710
a ray of light in Chengyi's life.

30:19.160 --> 30:20.120
And why do I say that?

30:20.200 --> 30:20.960
Because since Chengyi

30:20.990 --> 30:21.990
started dating you,

30:22.070 --> 30:23.560
he became like his old self.

30:23.630 --> 30:24.960
He was that happy

30:24.990 --> 30:26.660
and cheerful boy again.

30:26.690 --> 30:29.000
His dad and I are both so happy.

30:29.310 --> 30:30.670
I think

30:31.020 --> 30:32.250
you are

30:32.870 --> 30:34.020
the mature

30:34.390 --> 30:35.830
and elegant kind of girl.

30:36.440 --> 30:38.420
That's why I'm not afraid of letting you know those things.

30:38.520 --> 30:40.230
I know you wouldn't mind.

30:40.870 --> 30:41.720
Because

30:41.740 --> 30:43.560
everyone's experience

30:43.580 --> 30:45.580
is our precious treasure,

30:45.610 --> 30:46.870
am I right?

30:48.510 --> 30:49.060
Yes.

30:49.640 --> 30:50.760
But Auntie,

30:52.860 --> 30:53.980
actually,

30:54.120 --> 30:56.030
his girlfriend back in college

30:56.050 --> 30:56.920
was also me.

30:59.730 --> 31:00.780
But don't worry.

31:01.110 --> 31:01.950
Since we're

31:01.990 --> 31:03.430
back together,

31:04.030 --> 31:05.100
we'll

31:05.150 --> 31:05.800
make it work.

31:05.830 --> 31:07.030
I won't break his heart.

31:10.010 --> 31:10.960
Don't worry, Auntie.

31:15.330 --> 31:15.960
It's black.

31:15.990 --> 31:16.750
Come on.

31:16.800 --> 31:18.210
My specialty,

31:18.270 --> 31:19.350
Stir-fried Beef.

31:19.430 --> 31:20.010
Come on.

31:20.110 --> 31:20.900
This is my favorite.

31:20.900 --> 31:21.430
All the dishes have been served,

31:21.470 --> 31:22.030
right?

31:22.130 --> 31:23.270
Your favorite.

31:24.640 --> 31:26.150
I'd like to propose a toast

31:26.170 --> 31:27.510
before we start.

31:28.030 --> 31:29.620
I'd like to welcome Dr. Lu

31:29.650 --> 31:31.090
to our home.

31:31.190 --> 31:32.660
-Welcome.
-Come often.

31:32.750 --> 31:33.430
Come often.

31:33.510 --> 31:33.930
Okay.

31:34.030 --> 31:34.830
Come often.

31:34.850 --> 31:35.250
Alright.

31:35.280 --> 31:35.760
That's right.

31:35.780 --> 31:37.300
Thank you, Uncle and Auntie.

31:38.170 --> 31:39.160
Why don't you drink?

31:39.820 --> 31:40.760
I didn't file a report.

31:41.760 --> 31:42.770
Right.

31:43.510 --> 31:43.990
Come on.

31:44.060 --> 31:44.590
Let's eat.

31:44.610 --> 31:45.110
Here.

31:45.110 --> 31:46.190
-Come on.
-Try it.

31:46.190 --> 31:46.750
Yeah.

31:46.790 --> 31:48.350
-This is your favorite, right? Here.
-Stir-fried Beef.

31:48.630 --> 31:49.390
Okay.

31:50.390 --> 31:51.070
Here.

31:51.090 --> 31:51.880
I haven't used these chopsticks yet.

31:51.910 --> 31:52.430
Eat more prawns.

31:52.430 --> 31:53.230
How is it?

31:53.460 --> 31:54.570
So delicious.

31:55.300 --> 31:55.950
Uncle,

31:55.990 --> 31:57.190
your cooking is better than his.

31:57.210 --> 31:57.830
Of course.

31:57.830 --> 31:59.100
He's my master.

32:01.820 --> 32:02.910
You know?

32:03.660 --> 32:04.750
Yan

32:04.950 --> 32:06.050
was Chengyi's

32:06.070 --> 32:07.380
first girlfriend

32:07.490 --> 32:08.910
back in college.

32:14.090 --> 32:15.390
You already knew?

32:15.850 --> 32:17.020
Of course I knew.

32:17.770 --> 32:18.810
I noticed there was something going on between them

32:18.870 --> 32:20.470
when I was still hospitalized.

32:21.180 --> 32:23.220
Do you think I've been a police officer for so many years for nothing?

32:23.240 --> 32:24.240
So as soon as I was discharged,

32:24.330 --> 32:26.490
I did some investigation.

32:27.610 --> 32:28.160
Dad.

32:29.070 --> 32:30.320
You investigated me?

32:31.800 --> 32:33.050
You wouldn't even spare your own son?

32:33.070 --> 32:34.020
Of course.

32:34.300 --> 32:35.490
All your whereabouts

32:35.600 --> 32:37.730
are under my control.

32:37.750 --> 32:38.630
Oh my god.

32:38.810 --> 32:40.090
You're so scary.

32:42.800 --> 32:44.160
Lu.

32:44.250 --> 32:46.190
From now on,

32:46.390 --> 32:47.690
everything between you and Yi is up to you.

32:49.930 --> 32:50.550
After all,

32:50.550 --> 32:51.750
you saved my life,

32:51.750 --> 32:52.120
right?

32:52.160 --> 32:53.620
Don't say that.

32:53.650 --> 32:55.180
-That's what I should do.
-Yeah.

32:55.210 --> 32:56.460
It's my duty. It's my duty.

32:56.480 --> 32:57.090
But

32:57.120 --> 32:57.850
since you are

32:57.870 --> 32:59.010
my savior,

32:59.050 --> 33:01.100
help me to the end

33:01.260 --> 33:02.670
and do me another small favor,

33:02.690 --> 33:03.240
will you?

33:03.740 --> 33:04.690
No problem.

33:04.710 --> 33:06.110
Uncle, name it.

33:06.790 --> 33:07.680
I like

33:07.710 --> 33:08.840
Dr. Lu's personality.

33:08.870 --> 33:09.870
Straightforward.

33:09.930 --> 33:10.760
Yes.

33:12.950 --> 33:15.500
The small favor is that

33:16.830 --> 33:18.190
you two hurry up

33:18.270 --> 33:19.030
and get married,

33:19.090 --> 33:20.460
so that I can have a grand kid to have fun with,

33:20.550 --> 33:21.190
how's that?

33:21.600 --> 33:23.130
This is only her first time here.

33:23.200 --> 33:23.830
Dad.

33:23.880 --> 33:25.190
We've only started eating,

33:25.210 --> 33:26.320
and you're already talking about having a grand kid?

33:27.280 --> 33:28.110
Don't mind it. He was just kidding.

33:28.140 --> 33:28.930
Just kidding.

33:29.770 --> 33:31.420
One last thing.

33:31.720 --> 33:33.500
There's one more rule

33:34.200 --> 33:35.040
in the Jiang family.

33:36.200 --> 33:38.100
Listen to the team's order in work,

33:38.590 --> 33:40.780
and listen to your wife at home.

33:40.980 --> 33:41.830
Right, Son?

33:41.850 --> 33:42.810
That's right.

33:43.270 --> 33:44.270
Look.

33:44.330 --> 33:44.900
Let's eat.

33:44.960 --> 33:45.510
Yes.

33:46.110 --> 33:46.750
Look.

33:46.790 --> 33:47.710
Let's eat.

33:47.730 --> 33:48.130
Yes.

33:49.230 --> 33:50.830
You learned this pretty fast, huh?

33:52.070 --> 33:52.750
Eat.

33:52.770 --> 33:53.640
Okay.

33:53.670 --> 33:55.070
It's so delicious.

34:07.450 --> 34:08.889
You still haven't finished?

34:13.440 --> 34:14.389
What is this?

34:15.690 --> 34:16.659
This is...

34:16.690 --> 34:17.960
Can you understand?

34:18.159 --> 34:19.100
No.

34:22.199 --> 34:23.170
Look.

34:23.860 --> 34:25.600
The patient is a female,

34:25.940 --> 34:27.250
42 years old.

34:28.650 --> 34:31.179
Her blood pressure has been increasing for a year.

34:31.520 --> 34:32.880
She's taken medicine regularly

34:33.310 --> 34:34.210
for two months.

34:34.239 --> 34:35.739
We plan to do

34:35.830 --> 34:37.060
laparoscopy and endometrial biopsy

34:37.080 --> 34:39.380
under general anesthesia.

34:40.000 --> 34:42.100
Perform routine monitoring after entering the operating room.

35:05.680 --> 35:08.360
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

35:12.440 --> 35:13.170
Xiaoman.

35:13.360 --> 35:14.250
Where are you going?

35:14.270 --> 35:16.250
Why is Mr. Wen still not here yet?

35:16.470 --> 35:17.670
Mr. Wen is busy with his work.

35:17.670 --> 35:19.350
It's understandable that he can't come.

35:19.380 --> 35:20.570
Didn't he give us the tickets?

35:20.600 --> 35:21.520
I'll take you there, okay?

35:21.540 --> 35:22.310
No.

35:22.310 --> 35:23.770
I want Mr. Wen to take me.

35:23.870 --> 35:24.890
I'll take you. It's the same.

35:24.910 --> 35:25.950
-I'll cheer for you outside.
-Xiaoman.

35:26.810 --> 35:27.590
Ms. Lu.

35:27.610 --> 35:29.030
Do you know how to skate, too?

35:29.120 --> 35:30.750
I do.

35:30.780 --> 35:32.420
Can you take me there?

35:33.110 --> 35:34.250
Wait till my break time,

35:34.280 --> 35:35.060
and I can take you.

35:35.080 --> 35:35.840
Great.

35:36.170 --> 35:37.350
I can finally go skating.

35:37.380 --> 35:38.480
Thank you, Ms. Lu.

35:38.510 --> 35:39.190
Mom.

35:39.270 --> 35:41.060
Look, I can go skating too.

35:41.080 --> 35:42.080
Thank you.

35:42.140 --> 35:42.830
It's okay.

35:42.850 --> 35:44.120
I'll go get changed.

35:44.150 --> 35:45.000
Wait for me.

35:48.910 --> 35:49.660
So big.

35:50.970 --> 35:52.940
So many green peppers today.

35:53.070 --> 35:54.060
You're a grown woman,

35:54.110 --> 35:54.930
yet you're still such a picky eater.

35:55.030 --> 35:56.190
Why are you like my son?

35:56.540 --> 35:58.150
I watched too many cartoons when I was little.

35:58.190 --> 35:59.170
The protagonist in it doesn't eat green pepper.

35:59.210 --> 36:00.050
Neither do I.

36:00.740 --> 36:02.440
Do you think you're Crayon Shin-Chan?

36:03.400 --> 36:04.610
You've watched it too?

36:05.050 --> 36:06.010
Of course.

36:06.280 --> 36:07.810
I didn't like spinach when I was little.

36:07.940 --> 36:09.490
My mom had me watch Popeye the Sailor,

36:09.990 --> 36:10.910
and I thought

36:10.940 --> 36:12.650
I could grow muscle by eating spinach.

36:12.740 --> 36:13.930
But look,

36:14.160 --> 36:15.430
I still ended up so thin.

36:15.460 --> 36:16.540
And Garfield.

36:16.820 --> 36:17.650
When I was little,

36:17.670 --> 36:18.470
I really wanted to taste

36:18.490 --> 36:19.440
the lasagna in it.

36:19.470 --> 36:19.910
Yes.

36:20.020 --> 36:21.700
And Naruto's favorite Ramen.

36:21.960 --> 36:23.960
He always seems to enjoy it so happily.

36:24.470 --> 36:25.830
Whenever I'm in a bad mood,

36:25.850 --> 36:27.020
I'll watch Naruto eat Ramen.

36:27.130 --> 36:28.690
I always feel better after that.

36:28.710 --> 36:29.410
I even went out of my way to find out

36:29.440 --> 36:30.830
where to buy that Ramen,

36:30.860 --> 36:32.030
but I couldn't find it.

36:32.430 --> 36:33.460
Have you ever watched

36:33.490 --> 36:34.650
Chūka Ichiban?

36:34.920 --> 36:35.980
Of course.

36:36.890 --> 36:38.250
Every dish they cook looks delicious.

36:39.670 --> 36:40.840
And when the lid is opened,

36:40.860 --> 36:42.140
it's all shiny.

36:42.380 --> 36:44.180
I like Mapo Tofu the most.

36:44.270 --> 36:45.720
My favorite is their Egg Fried Rice.

36:45.750 --> 36:47.430
Every grain is distinct!

36:47.600 --> 36:48.500
Right!

36:48.680 --> 36:56.740
[Criminal Psychology]

36:55.470 --> 36:56.470
How did you do it?

36:59.790 --> 37:00.620
Just...

37:00.800 --> 37:02.450
How did you

37:02.480 --> 37:04.070
perfectly avoid

37:04.090 --> 37:06.540
all the right choices?

37:08.110 --> 37:09.530
What is the probability of that?

37:11.240 --> 37:11.960
All wrong?

37:13.350 --> 37:13.770
But

37:13.810 --> 37:15.350
I did it very carefully.

37:15.920 --> 37:16.710
But

37:16.910 --> 37:18.620
I counted on my feeling for most questions.

37:20.690 --> 37:21.810
Feelings?

37:22.790 --> 37:23.590
I worked so hard

37:23.660 --> 37:24.850
and highlighted so many key points for you,

37:24.870 --> 37:26.350
yet you told me you solved them basically based on feelings?

37:26.370 --> 37:27.260
Have you read it or not?

37:27.310 --> 37:28.230
I have.

37:28.250 --> 37:29.730
Isn't it written clearly that

37:29.880 --> 37:32.100
from the original family to bad habits,

37:32.120 --> 37:33.850
then to strong emotional changes,

37:33.870 --> 37:35.340
and eventually it developed a motive for murder?

37:35.360 --> 37:36.270
Do you not understand

37:36.350 --> 37:36.920
the logic

37:36.950 --> 37:38.550
and the way of thinking?

37:38.920 --> 37:39.960
Have you read it carefully?

37:40.030 --> 37:40.390
I...

37:40.390 --> 37:41.340
What's your college entrance exam score?

37:41.710 --> 37:43.790
I didn't take the college entrance exam. I went to technical secondary school.

37:50.690 --> 37:52.800
Then it's understandable that

37:52.990 --> 37:54.070
this is a bit difficult for you.

37:55.260 --> 37:56.630
But you got this question right.

37:56.710 --> 37:57.270
Not bad.

37:57.360 --> 37:58.610
It's even a word problem.

38:00.420 --> 38:01.750
I didn't solve it myself.

38:03.270 --> 38:05.020
When I was solving this question that day,

38:05.300 --> 38:06.200
Mr. Wen was here too.

38:06.230 --> 38:07.310
He told me the answer.

38:08.830 --> 38:09.630
Wen Peng?

38:09.870 --> 38:10.470
Yes.

38:13.010 --> 38:13.880
Professor Yu.

38:14.310 --> 38:15.350
